OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1778217985
OL,3,CWoman raped by two men on street in
OL,4,CDoncaster
OL,6,FA 48-year-old man was arrested on
OL,7,FSunday on suspicion of rape, while a
OL,8,F45-year-old man was arrested on
OL,9,Fsuspicion of sexual assault. Both have
OL,10,Fbeen released on bail pending further
OL,11,Finvestigation.
OL,13,FThe victim is being supported by
OL,14,Fspecialist officers.
OL,16,FPolice said both suspects are white.
OL,17,FOne is around 5ft 10ins tall, of
OL,18,Faverage build and bald. The other was
OL,19,Fdescribed as around 6ft tall and slim.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
