PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1778217985
OL,3,CWoman raped by two men on street in
OL,4,CDoncaster
OL,6,FDet Ch Insp Susannah Wagstaff, of
OL,7,FSouth Yorkshire Police, said: "We know
OL,8,Fthat news of this incident will cause
OL,9,Fconcern in our local communities but I
OL,10,Fwant to reassure you that we have a
OL,11,Fteam of detectives working hard to
OL,12,Fprogress this investigation."
OL,14,FThe force asked anyone with
OL,15,Finformation on the assault to contact
OL,16,Fthem on 101.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
